Title: 4-Port USB3.0 4K DisplayPort Triple Display KVMP™ Switch - CS1964, ATEN Desktop KVM Switches
Description: The ATEN CS1964 optimizes your desktop so you can effortlessly manage a triple-display multimedia workstation with instant, user-friendly access to four computers via a single USB keyboard, USB mouse and three HDMI monitors supporting resolutions up to 4K DCI (4096 x 2160 @ 60Hz).The CS1964 is equipped with ATEN’s patented Video DynaSync™ technology which optimizes display resolution, speeds up switching between systems, and ensures that windows opened on an extended desktop will not revert to their default configurations on the main display when switching between ports, providing a smooth and uninterrupted user experience. It features a USB 3.1 GEN hub for data transfer rates up to 5 Gbps, allowing you to accelerate multimedia operations with ease, as well as N-key Rollover, offering support for up to 15 simultaneous keystrokes without ghosting or jamming. | CS1964 | ATEN Corporate Headquarters
